1130
01:26:59,423 --> 01:27:00,595
Yes, you bring.

1131
01:27:05,095 --> 01:27:06,313
Okay, next. Let's go.

1132
01:27:08,056 --> 01:27:09,979
- Let's go!
- I'm coming.

1133
01:27:14,062 --> 01:27:15,150
Take care for him.

1134
01:27:15,230 --> 01:27:16,482
- See you next time.
- <i>Gracias.</i>

1135
01:27:18,483 --> 01:27:20,076
