01:28:37,896 --> 01:28:40,741
I really love you. You're such a funny guy.

1145
01:28:41,066 --> 01:28:42,158
Hilarious.

1146
01:28:42,400 --> 01:28:45,904
Like I said, you're too much a nice guy

