1169
01:29:57,225 --> 01:29:58,226
Me?

1170
01:29:58,310 --> 01:30:00,483
This is the situation.

1171
01:30:00,645 --> 01:30:02,568
I don't know exactly what,

1172
01:30:02,731 --> 01:30:04,734
but something big, very big,

1173
